Esc / Ctrl+c    | NORMAL MODE
i               | INSERT MODE (Before cursor)
a               | INSERT MODE (After cursor)
o               | INSERT MODE (Open a new line below)
v               | VISUAL MODE (Character selection)
V               | VISUAL LINE MODE (Line selection)
Ctrl+v          | VISUAL BLOCK MODE (Column/vertical)
:wq             | Write and Quit
:q!             | Quit without saving
:w              | Write
:q              | Quit
:wa             | Write all open files
h               | Move Left
j               | Move Down
k               | Move Up
l               | Move Right
0               | Move to the start of the line
^               | Move to the first character of the line
$               | Move to the end of the current line
w               | Move forward to the start of the next word
e               | Move forward to the end of the next word
b               | Move backward to the start of the previous word
gg              | Move to the start of the file
G               | Move to the end of the file
:N              | Jump to line number N (e.g., :42)
H               | Move cursor to Top of the screen
M               | Move cursor to Middle of the screen
L               | Move cursor to Bottom of the screen
y               | Copy (Yank) selected text
yy              | Copy (Yank) the entire current line
Y               | Copy from cursor to the end of the line
p               | Paste copied text after the cursor
P               | Paste copied text before the cursor
"+y             | Copy selected text to the system clipboard
"+p             | Paste text from the system clipboard
d               | Delete (Cut) selected text
dd              | Delete (Cut) the entire current line
dw              | Delete from cursor to the start of the next word
x               | Delete character under the cursor
r               | Replace a single character under the cursor
R               | Enter REPLACE MODE (Overwrite text)
u               | Undo last action
Ctrl+r          | Redo last undone action
.               | Repeat the last editing command
ci"             | Change inside double quotes ""
ci(             | Change inside parentheses ()
cit             | Change inside XML/HTML tags
di"             | Delete everything inside double quotes ""
yi"             | Copy everything inside double quotes ""
*               | Search forward for the word under the cursor
/               | Search forward for a custom pattern
?               | Search backward for a custom pattern
n               | Go to the next search match
N               | Go to the previous search match
:%s/old/new/g   | Find and replace 'old' with 'new' globally
:%s/old/new/gc  | Find and replace globally, asking for confirm
:Explore        | Open the built-in file manager (Netrw)
:split or :sp   | Split screen horizontally 
:vsplit or :vsp | Split screen vertically
Ctrl+w w        | Cycle/switch focus between open split windows
Ctrl+w q        | Close the current split window
>>              | Indent the current line
<<              | Unindent the current line
Ctrl+n          | INSERT : Autocomplete
:e ~/file       | Edit file in buffer
:ls             | Show files in buffer
:b npfl/123     | Move n-next buffer, p-previous,first,las
:r ~/file       | Read the file content to current buffer
